  TERM Creating a Web Client 48004
  Creating a Web Client You create an WebClient instance with default options as follows WebClient client = WebClient . create ( vertx ) ; If you want to configure options for the client, you create it as follows WebClientOptions options = new WebClientOptions () . setUserAgent ( " My-App/1.2.3 " ) ; options . setKeepAlive ( false ) ; WebClient client = WebClient . create 
  
