.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow and -Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"5.0.1 resolves Vert.x core 5.0.1 with Netty 4.2.2.Final; omitting the Java 25 unsafe/reflection-access runtime properties may reproduce the native-image runtime failure seen for 5.0.0/5.0.1.\",\n    \"OAuth2WebClient is part of the artifact API but depends on optional io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2; avoid OAuth2-specific tests unless the workflow deliberately adds that optional dependency.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08c3680ff9754fbc016a3ffbe51098819492238deb96b69ad8\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 922, "output": 902, "cacheRead": 27648, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29472, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782578138343, "responseId": "resp_08c3680ff9754fbc016a3ffbdacd048194b407b8e16256bb00"}, "toolResults": []}
